      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SACRED INGOT (7) resumes with the 1000m trial under his belt at the Sapphire Coast. Beaten a nose here four-back over the mile and can sprint well fresh from the good gate. ROY KELTON (1) kept safe in betting on debut with a respectable come from behind second over 1300m at Goulburn in a tougher race. Will benefit from that experience and shapes as the main danger. MANZOBEEL (3) having her third race start today and will find this an easier test. Slow into stride and got further back than intended with a battling eighth over 1500m at Albury. Can improve quickly and take a hand in the finish. ARCANA IMPERII (4) struck trouble at the start and never got into the contest with a poor eleventh over 1460m at Queanbeyan. Had excuses last start and gets his chance with the sharp weight drop. TSARINA DIAMONDS (9) found the 1300m too short first-up and assess on her narrow second two-back at the Sapphire Coast. Keep safe.",
